root: ^What delays our subordinates? I cannot see them anywhere.
^You mean what delays your subordinates. If we debated, you would have realised that they are inferior. Mine however, shall appear at any second.
^What’s this? It appears that one of your kind has gone rogue.
^Oh stars, the mission is in jeopardy! Hurry, we must abduct it before it reaches the cow creatures and alerts the humans of our presence!
^Hmm. It may not be the only one with the wrong idea…
